{"tid":1462493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地係咪搞錯左個目標？","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:01.000Z","uid":229886,"like":90,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"92609a87ae6bf1a0eacfc28c7049e158a3bf35f6","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"一開始玩機場係和理非<br />\n不合作唔屬於和理非<br />\n講真不合作真係好難睇<br />\n我地知你做緊乜<br />\n遊客只係知你塞鳩佢<br />\n我地要做既係要令機管局cancel班機<br />\n唔係由你地去cancel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到唔係你想點就點<br />\n可唔可以聽下人講？<br />\n有d人帶風向話唔夠人，所以不合作<br />\n喂屌你老母呢到機場黎架，你估港鐵啊？<br />\n你知唔知主動塞入口係好難睇？<br />\n唔夠人咪靜坐宣傳囉<br />\n不嬲都咁做架啦<br />\n所有野唔係非黑即白<br />\n做不合作可唔可以用下個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cada53bac3b3b50453e9d89391a62d89bdc183","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176019b7d671c6ac7b697005828eb95d38ae42dc","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241d5c2cac091b7720068950296bd3200e58089f","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ab2df5a7cdfefbeca24bb16d58adefafc13b03","tid":1462493,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"309da2d5a13f035f646ee639be62770ceb8f05f6","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"唔撚block啊<br />\n係jam啊<br />\n識唔識啊"},{"pid":"3a09128ec3ec9ea3ba891ed38f0cb21929c84cbe","tid":1462493,"uid":297230,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime