理收賠償<br />\n但你阻到佢上唔到機係佢自己賠<br />\n會令佢地強烈反感<br />\n甚至回國後喪屌示威者<br />\n屌到外國政客都唔敢出聲撑香港<br />\n我地而家要癱瘓亦要爭取國際支持<br />\n有人試圖阻旅客<br />\n請溫和地解釋點解唔應該呢個時候咁做<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n不過樓主態度可以好d<br />\n屌人只會愈來愈分化<br />\n明白大家一時三刻會好勞氣<br />\n但勞氣前諗一諗自己嘅語氣係對件事好定反效果<br />\n錫返唔好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"我幾時有屌人？<br />\n係有個波台友係咁針對我<br />\n人多癱瘓<br />\n人少宣傳<br />\n不互屌"},{"pid":"e7494d27021b399b93a67d27bf968c1c1891e247","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a157f5377e869c3bd727f6535be2d90fe6e0b3bc","tid":1462493,"uid":144996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99e3a773e033df8d0ec9ed6a546a5d0a8d918c14","tid":1462493,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d20505ad56bdd74f822b2d8a5fccfc72bfcfbb0","tid":1462493,"uid":144996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"我唔洗翻工？<br />\n點解仲可以咁自私？<br />\n你都識講多人先癱瘓<br />\n咁你唔嚟？<br />\n多人就係咁嚟㗎啦<br />\n我入 你入 佢入 叫埋身邊嘅一齊入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"個個識講夠人就塞爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個就去返工<br />\n塞咩呀 塞爆金鐘站呀?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"係啊 好撚搞笑㗎佢地<br />\n自己冇嚟仲好似好合理咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"波台圍爐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0300b5454321fe8861e5befe5ddb6786637c7f","tid":1462493,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46949781339622d7406e2b4a1816da6ecb132ad","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee0437248f0ae0d29e5623b32bee9be5465ec7fa","tid":1462493,"uid":249187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"推 我地目的唔係阻人上機 係文宣啊！<br />\n琴日多人所以癱瘓機場係bonus黎