-size: x-large;\">誘餌</span></strong>，比大家以為機場癱瘓會對政府有好大損失，而令大家目標由<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「宣傳五大訴求+黑警治港」</span></span></strong>去到變成「癱瘓機場」, 一定唔可以變成咁. <br />\n<br />\n我地要做既, 只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>等政府/警隊繼續出醜!</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n同埋黎緊9月<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國都會討論香港關係法同人權法,</span></strong></span> 所以我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守住個民意</span></span></span>到嗰個時刻. <br />\n<br />\n旅客口耳相傳對我地好重要，亦係我地重要既盟友<br />\n<br />\n如果見到旅客，無論黎定係走都好，不妨同佢地講下香港發生咩事，同埋我地香港人既五大訴求係乜。<br />\n<br />\n不妨加埋以下問候句: <br />\nArrival: Welcome to Hong Kong! <br />\n<br />\nDeparture: Thanks for coming! Please share what happened in Hong Kong back to your country and friends!<br />\n<br />\n順便同佢地講聲，話可能會有人阻到佢地上機，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>阻到佢地上機好有可能係警方假扮示威者搞事，之前啲示威活動都有過呢種情況</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n再講多次: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定唔可以阻旅客上機! 旅客係我地既盟友</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999, 小弟文筆唔好, 希望大家明白, 請幫手推或者開新post!"},{"pid":"5766dcf397f68cc9d6295fdb09f727b6e54f829e","tid":1462493,"uid":145983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd39d4af2fca2737ba9edacb8f21c7b4ee396e2","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627ce847100df8196b25c2302392a362618da759","tid":1462493,"uid":47303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0275e411ea518c0160303edff069f5fef856e69b","tid":1462493,"uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"咁你點解唔塞撚住個閘口唔比人上機？<br />\n衝埋禁區啦，不合作啊嘛<br />\n屌你都廢鳩事<br />\n有你呢d吳卓羲係到<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦 和理非日日返工 放假先抗爭 政府一定怕你地GE<img src=\"/assets